 *   - WebSocket route at /stream (protocol per ws.ts).
 *   - Exclusive 127.0.0.1 binding (D57, RC: no 0.0.0.0 code path).
 *
 * Design invariants:
 *   - All reads use db.reader() (read-only connection).
